Subject: Re: [T2] Audi/Vanagon seats in a '74?

Howdy,
I replaced my stock 78 front seats with early 80s vanagon seats. The vanagon
seats are more comfortable and have superior innards, at least with regard to
durability/longevity.
Regards,
Chris

